        <span>Credit Cards</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Credit Cards</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Find the perfect credit card that matches your lifestyle and spending habits. Compare features, rewards, and benefits from India's top banks — all in one place.</p>
      <div class="hero-highlights">
