        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-infinity"></i> Lifetime Free Options
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content-main">

          <!-- Overview -->
          <h2>Credit Cards Overview</h2>
          <p>A credit card is a powerful financial tool that lets you make purchases, earn rewards, and build a strong credit history. Whether you're looking for cashback on everyday spends, travel perks, or a way to manage large purchases through EMIs — there's a card for every need.</p>
          <p>At TrueCred Loan Expert, we help you compare 50+ credit cards from India's leading banks including SBI, HDFC, ICICI, Axis Bank, and more. Our smart comparison engine ensures you find the best card based on your income, spending pattern, and credit score.</p>

          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Earn reward points on every purchase and redeem them for gifts, vouchers, or statement credits</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Get cashback of up to 5% on online shopping, groceries, dining, and fuel spends</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Enjoy complimentary airport lounge access with premium cards</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Convert large purchases into easy EMIs with low interest rates</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Build your credit score with responsible usage and timely repayments</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Avail exclusive discounts on travel bookings, entertainment, and dining</li>
          </ul>

          <!-- Card Categories -->
          <h2>Explore Credit Card Categories</h2>
          <p>Choose from a wide range of credit card types designed to suit different financial needs and lifestyles.</p>

          <div class="products-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); margin: 24px 0 40px;">
            <div class="product-card">
              <div class="product-icon"><i class="fas fa-gift"></i></div>
              <h3>Rewards Cards</h3>
              <p>Earn points on every swipe and redeem for exciting gifts, vouchers, and travel bookings</p>
              <span class="product-cta">Explore Cards <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
            </div>
            <div class="product-card">
              <div class="product-icon"><i class="fas fa-indian-rupee-sign"></i></div>
              <h3>Cashback Cards</h3>
              <p>Get instant cashback on groceries, online shopping, bill payments, and more</p>
              <span class="product-cta">Explore Cards <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
            </div>
            <div class="product-card">
              <div class="product-icon"><i class="fas fa-plane"></i></div>
              <h3>Travel Cards</h3>
              <p>Complimentary lounge access, air miles, zero forex markup, and travel insurance</p>
              <span class="product-cta">Explore Cards <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
            </div>
            <div class="product-card">
              <div class="product-icon"><i class="fas fa-gas-pump"></i></div>
              <h3>Fuel Cards</h3>
              <p>Save up to 5% on fuel purchases with surcharge waivers at all petrol pumps</p>
              <span class="product-cta">Explore Cards <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
            </div>
            <div class="product-card">
              <div class="product-icon"><i class="fas fa-infinity"></i></div>
              <h3>Lifetime Free Cards</h3>
              <p>No joining fee, no annual charges — enjoy premium benefits absolutely free forever</p>
              <span class="product-cta">Explore Cards <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
            </div>
            <div class="product-card">
              <div class="product-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
              <h3>Secured Cards</h3>
              <p>Build your credit score with a card backed by a fixed deposit — 100% approval guaranteed</p>
              <span class="product-cta">Explore Cards <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Rate Comparison Table -->
          <h2>Compare Popular Credit Cards</h2>
          <p>Here's a quick comparison of some of the most popular credit cards in India to help you make an informed decision.</p>

          <table class="rate-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Card</th>
                <th>Joining Fee</th>
                <th>Annual Fee</th>
                <th>Reward Rate</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>SBI SimplyCLICK</strong></td>
                <td>₹499</td>
                <td>₹499</td>
                <td>10X rewards on partner sites</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>HDFC Millennia</strong></td>
                <td>₹1,000</td>
                <td>₹1,000</td>
                <td>5% cashback on online spends</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Axis Flipkart</strong></td>
                <td>₹500</td>
                <td>₹500</td>
                <td>5% cashback on Flipkart</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>ICICI Amazon Pay</strong></td>
