          <!-- Eligibility -->
          <h2>Credit Card Eligibility</h2>
          <p>Meeting the basic eligibility criteria improves your chances of instant approval. Here are the general requirements most banks look for:</p>

          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Age:</strong> Minimum 21 years and maximum 60 years (salaried) or 65 years (self-employed)</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Income:</strong> Minimum monthly income of ₹15,000 for salaried or ₹2.5 lakh annual income for self-employed</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Credit Score:</strong> CIBIL score of 700 or above for regular cards; secured cards available for lower scores</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Employment:</strong> Must be a salaried employee, self-employed professional, or business owner</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Documents:</strong> PAN Card, Aadhaar Card, income proof (salary slips or ITR), and address proof</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Nationality:</strong> Indian resident or NRI with valid Indian documentation</li>
          </ul>

          <!-- How to Apply -->
          <h3>How to Apply for a Credit Card</h3>
          <p>Getting a credit card through TrueCred is simple, fast, and completely digital. Follow these easy steps:</p>

          <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <h4>Compare Cards</h4>
              <p>Browse and compare 50+ cards based on rewards, fees, and benefits</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
